        public void Transform(caffe.FloatBlob input_blob,
                      caffe.FloatBlob transformed_blob)
        \brief Applies the same transformation defined in the data layer's transform_param block to all the num images in a input_blob.
        Parameters:
        input_blob - A Blob containing the data to be transformed. It applies the same transformation to all the num images in the blob.
        transformed_blob - This is destination blob, it will contain as many images as the input blob. It can be part of top blob's data.
